description:
SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE VIDEOS! :)
Enjoy my very first lego clip!
This is the Easter Story made out of talking Lego people. It is gotten out of the Message Bible. If you would like to use this please let me know. And if you enjoyed it please like as I put alot of work into making this video. Please let me know what you think :) or if you have any questions about this just let me know. I hope you got inspired by this story. Please subscribe to show your support

If you liked this video you can watch my David and Goliath in lego!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=29LisuzEGzk

and The Christmas Story in Lego!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LuWhev6VRiM
